{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Proximity","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Proximity_Events","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>這是一個實驗中的功能</strong><br>此功能在某些瀏覽器尚在開發中，請參考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">兼容表格</a>以得到不同瀏覽器用的前輟。</p></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"摘要","title":"摘要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>近距 (Proximity) 事件可迅速感測出使用者靠近裝置，並迅速做出反應。舉例來說，當使用者接通來電並將裝置靠近耳朵時，智慧型手機隨即關閉螢幕。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>備註：</strong> 顯然裝置必須具備近距感測器 (Proximity sensor)，此 API 才能發揮作用。而目前幾乎只有行動裝置搭載接近感測器。若裝置並未搭載感測器，則雖同樣可支援，但永遠不會觸發此類事件。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"近距事件","title":"近距事件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>只要近距感測器測得「裝置」與「物體」之間的距離改變時，就會通知瀏覽器這項變化。而只要瀏覽器獲得通知，隨即啟動 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">DeviceProximityEvent (en-US)</a> 以因應任何變化；或啟動 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UserProximityEvent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">UserProximityEvent (en-US)</a> 以因應簡單的變化。</p>\n<p>透過 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">addEventListener (en-US)</a> 函式 (使用 <code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/deviceproximity\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">deviceproximity</a></code> 或 <code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/userproximity\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">userproximity</a></code> 事件名稱)；或將事件處理器 (Event handler) 附掛至 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/window.ondeviceproximity\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>window.ondeviceproximity</code></a> 或 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/window.onuserproximity\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>window.onuserproximity</code></a> 屬性，均可於 <code>window 物件層級就擷取到此事件。</code></p>\n<p>在擷取事件之後，事件物件將可存取不同的資訊：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">DeviceProximityEvent (en-US)</a> 事件透過本身的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent.value\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>value</code></a> 屬性，可提供裝置與物體之間的確實距離。另透過本身的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent.min\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>min</code></a> 與 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent.max\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>max</code></a> 屬性，則能設定「裝置測得某物」的最近與最遠距離。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UserProximityEvent\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">UserProximityEvent (en-US)</a> 事件則提供粗略的距離，並以 Boolean 值呈現。物體靠近時，<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/UserProximityEvent.near\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\"><code>UserProximityEvent.near</code></a> 屬性即為 <code>true</code>；物體遠離則為 <code>false。</code></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"範例","title":"範例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'userproximity'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>near<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// let's power off the screen</span>\n    navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mozPower<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screenEnabled <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Otherwise, let's power on the screen</span>\n    navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>mozPower<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screenEnabled <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"規範","title":"規範","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此功能不再有望成為標準。它的歷史規範仍然<a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/proximity/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">可用</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另可參閱","title":"另可參閱","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceProximityEvent\"><code>DeviceProximityEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/UserProximityEvent\"><code>UserProximityEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/deviceproximity\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">deviceproximity</a></code></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Reference/Events/userproximity\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">userproximity</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"摘要","id":"摘要"},{"text":"近距事件","id":"近距事件"},{"text":"範例","id":"範例"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"另可參閱","id":"另可參閱"}],"summary":"近距 (Proximity) 事件可迅速感測出使用者靠近裝置，並迅速做出反應。舉例來說，當使用者接通來電並將裝置靠近耳朵時，智慧型手機隨即關閉螢幕。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Proximity Events","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Proximity","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Proximity Events","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Proximity Events","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/proximity_events","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/proximity_events/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Proximity_Events","title":"Proximity"}],"pageTitle":"Proximity - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}